 Galvatron turned to Guiledart. I will go to her now. She could be of use to 
us. I know she is the hurt type. The time when Magnus was apart of me I saw 
what he saw in her. So hopefully she shall become one of us." he turned into 
his dragon mode. And flew off and sent a message to her typed. "Hello my 
darling. I am interested in you joining me and my men. I will be there to 
meet you soon."

--part1_f4.ddf18a1.28a9faf3_boundary
